      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          In 2018, I sat in a board meeting and couldn't answer a simple question:
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">"Is our wellbeing strategy actually working?"</span>
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          That embarrassing moment changed everything. I spent the next 5 years building the frameworks I wish I'd had—frameworks now used by FTSE companies and NHS Trusts across the UK.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
          I help boards because I've been the director who didn't have answers. Now I make sure you do.
        </p>
      </div>
